==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Irresistible
<hw>Ir`re*sist"i*ble</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Pref.
<ets>ir-</ets> not + <ets>resistible</ets>: cf. F.
<ets>irr⟦eacute⟧sistible</ets>.]</ety> <def>That can not be successfully
resisted or opposed; superior to opposition; resistless; overpowering;
<as>as, an <ex>irresistible</ex> attraction</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>An <qex>irresistible</qex> law of our nature impels us to seek
happiness.</q> <rj><qau>J. M. Mason.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Irresistibleness</ent>⟦br⟧
